  <entry>
    <title>推荐一个看番软件</title>
    <url>/posts/567274b5.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>推荐一个我经常用的看番软件：Animeko（<a href="https://myani.org/">https://myani.org/</a>或<a href="https://github.com/open-ani/animeko/">https://github.com/open-ani/animeko/</a>）。<br>
这个软件集成了Bangumi，登录Bangumi账号后，再使用这个软件看番就会自动把进度同步。同时，这个软件一键点格子比在Bangumi上快多了。而且这个软件会读取弹弹Play的弹幕。最爽的是，这个软件支持长按倍速，再也不用担心看厕纸不能快进了。</p>
<p>此外，分享一下关于数据源的经验（当前版本4.0.1，不确定后续版本是否相同）。<br>
先讲一下思路。<br>
有很多在线看番网站的模板大差不差，因此可以在已经给出的数据源中找出与你想用的数据源相似的，然后依葫芦画瓢改一改就行。其实大部分都不用改。<br>
给出一个我搞好的例子。以下是次元城的数据源。（2024年12月15日更新：自带次元城数据源了）</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;mediaSources&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">[</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;factoryId&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;web-selector&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;version&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="number">2</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;arguments&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;次元城&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;description&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;iconUrl&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;https://www.cyc-anime.net/upload/site/20240319-1/25e700991446a527804c82a744731b60.png&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;searchConfig&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;searchUrl&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;https://www.cyc-anime.net/search.html?wd=&#123;keyword&#125;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;searchUseOnlyFirstWord&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;searchRemoveSpecial&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;rawBaseUrl&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;subjectFormatId&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;indexed&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectorSubjectFormatA&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectLists&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;body &gt; div.box-width &gt; div &gt; div.row-9 &gt; div &gt; div &gt; div.right.rel.flex-auto &gt; div.thumb-content &gt; div.thumb-txt.cor4.hide&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;preferShorterName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectorSubjectFormatIndexed&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectNames&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;body &gt; .box-width .search-box .thumb-content &gt; .thumb-txt&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectLinks&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;body &gt; .box-width .search-box .thumb-menu &gt; a&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;preferShorterName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectorSubjectFormatJsonPathIndexed&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectLinks&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;$[*][&#x27;url&#x27;, &#x27;link&#x27;]&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectNames&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;$[*][&#x27;title&#x27;,&#x27;name&#x27;]&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;preferShorterName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;channelFormatId&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;index-grouped&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectorChannelFormatFlattened&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectChannelNames&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;.anthology-tab &gt; .swiper-wrapper a&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;matchChannelName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;^(?&lt;ch&gt;.+?)(\\d+)?$&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectEpisodeLists&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;.anthology-list-box&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectEpisodesFromList&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;a&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectEpisodeLinksFromList&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;matchEpisodeSortFromName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;第\\s*(?&lt;ep&gt;.+)\\s*[话集]&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectorChannelFormatNoChannel&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectEpisodes&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;.anthology-list-play&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectEpisodeLinks&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;matchEpisodeSortFromName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;第\\s*(?&lt;ep&gt;.+)\\s*[话集]&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;filterByEpisodeSort&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;filterBySubjectName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;selectMedia&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;distinguishSubjectName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;distinguishChannelName&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;matchVideo&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;enableNestedUrl&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;matchNestedUrl&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;^.+(m3u8|vip|xigua\\.php).+\\?&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;matchVideoUrl&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;(^http(s)?:\\/\\/(?!.*http(s)?:\\/\\/).+((\\.mp4)|(\\.mkv)|(m3u8)).*(\\?.+)?)|(akamaized)|(bilivideo.com)&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;cookies&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;quality=1080&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;addHeadersToVideo&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="attr">&quot;referer&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span><span class="attr">&quot;userAgent&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/58.0.3029.110 Safari/537.3&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="punctuation">]</span><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>记得测试一下是否正常。如果不正常，可能是次元城挂了，也可能是你的网络犯病，也可能是换网址了。<br>
我建议使用<a href="https://www.cycity.pro/">https://www.cycity.pro/</a>这个地址发布页看看次元城的最新网址。这个网站还是很不错的，广告影响不大。</p>
<p>当然，仅仅使用自带的源一般就够了。新番可以用BT，老番就老老实实用在线源吧。<br>
以我这里的网络，稀饭动漫和漫次元是比较好的，清晰度高且无广告。</p>
<p>祝大家看番顺利。</p>
]]></content>
